Fudan University Affiliated Pediatric Hospital is working with the national neonatal department to develop guidelines for the diagnosis and treatment of neonatal infections according to the accumulated experience of the project, so as to provide reference and guidance for the standardized diagnosis and treatment of newborn infections in China.
