Beijing News (Reporter Ni Wei) The State Administration of Radio and Television issued the "Notice on the Implementation of the Special Remediation of Radio and Television Advertising" on September 29, and carried out special rectification of radio and television advertising from now until the end of this year.
The rectification content includes advertisements with low content, low taste and low taste, and medical health programs that broadcast problems without record management.
