Specifically, there are advertisements with orientation problems; advertisements with low content, low taste; advertisements with overtime and non-provisional problems; advertisements that exaggerate false propaganda, mislead the audience, or publish in disguise with the form of programs, medical, medical devices, health food, cosmetics, beauty and other advertisements, and medical health programs that broadcast problems without the record management; there are advertisements that exaggerate false propaganda, mislead the audience, and induce the audience to be deceived.There are problems in the length and frequency of public service advertisements that do not meet the requirements of the regulations; there are problems of inadequate advertising broadcast management system, laxity in censorship and responsibility; there are other illegal and illegal advertisements.
The rectification work will be fully covered in the country, the rectification and standardization requirements to the full implementation of the requirements of the rectification and norms to all levels of radio and television media, the frequency of each channel, the program columns and periods, "no blind spots, no dead ends, no exceptions."
The notice requires that the administrative departments of radio and television at all levels should deal with all kinds of illegal and illegal advertisements found in supervision and inspection in strict accordance with the "Measures for the Handling of Illegalities of Radio and Television Broadcasting Institutions" of the General Administration.
For serious violations, it is necessary to give serious treatment such as exhortation to talk, report criticism, suspend advertising broadcast until the suspension of frequency channels broadcast, and expose it to the public as appropriate.
