Lawyer with an axe in court session?
The news is really exciting at first glance, and it also exploded in the legal circle.
Fujian Quanzhou City China and France subsequently fined the lawyers involved 500 yuan and suggested in writing that the Quanzhou Bar Association investigate and deal with it.
According to the Beijing News, a few days ago, the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association issued an official notice that the behavior of the two lawyers does not involve illegal violations and is not punished according to law.
From the multi-party report, the treatment of Quanzhou City Law Association is not to protect short or confrontation, but has been recognized by the Quanzhou Middle Court.
An incident that could have triggered tensions within the legal community was finally properly resolved.
The reversal of the matter stems from a more complete truth restoration: the axe carried by the lawyer involved is the same style and model as the defendant's murder weapon, but it is not bladed, only to provide auxiliary evidence in the cross-examination process, and there is no act of intimidation or "endangering the court's security" subjective intention.
There are four very important details to pay attention to in determining whether the behavior of the lawyers involved is illegal: first, the local court has only shown the axe photo, from the defense point of view, the original of the axe is necessary; second, the axe is purchased only 1 hour before the trial, not the lawyer does not want to seek the consent of the judge, but objectively failed to contact the judge; third, the whole axe was not over-used or improperly used; fourth, the lawyer was first.
Comprehensively combining these circumstances, it can be seen that the lawyers involved "showcase in court with axes" have nothing to do with it, but only to defend.
After clarifying the whole facts, the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association did not push the boat along the water, but resisted the pressure and made a decision not to punish.
This decision also stands the test of facts and laws.
As for bringing the axe of the controlled tool to the court without the permission of the court, it is indeed prone to anxiety and misunderstanding.
For safety and prudence, the previous fines and judicial recommendations of the Quanzhou Middle Court are also understandable.
In order to safeguard the dignity of lawyers and prevent individual courts from using difficult lawyers, the Supreme People's Court issued the Rules for Security Inspection of Judicial Police in the People's Courts in 2014, which established the principle that lawyers do not need to conduct personal safety checks in court.
Since the issuance of the rule, the majority of lawyers have led by example, and there are few incidents that endanger the security of the court due to security loopholes.
In rare cases such as Quanzhou, as long as it is communicated in a spirit of mutual respect and understanding, misunderstandings are not difficult to eliminate.
As a self-regulatory organization in the lawyer industry, the Bar Association has the dual mission of disciplining illegality and safeguarding legality.
In the past, individual legal organizations were criticized for their emphasis on punishment and lost their protection.
The decision of the Quanzhou Law Association, both in terms of process and results, is commendable and sets an example for more lawyers to perform their duties correctly.
From October 1, which tax benefits will affect our wallets?
Xinhua News Agency, Shanghai, October 1 (Reporter Sang Tong) The new personal income tax law will come into effect on January 1, 2019, in order to allow the broad masses of the people to enjoy tax reduction dividends as soon as possible, from October 1, the actual wage and salary income of taxpayers will be deducted according to the starting point of 5,000 yuan per month, and the new tax rate table will be applied.
With the landing of the New Deal, what are the benefits that will affect the people's money bags?
Benefit 1: The tax reduction rate of wages and salaries is obvious
Taxpayers who receive salary after October 1 can deduct the basic deduction fee of 5,000 yuan / month and apply the new tax rate table, and most taxpayers have different degrees of tax cuts, especially for low- and middle-income people.
According to the tax reduction table of different income groups, after deducting the "three insurances and one gold", the monthly income of 8000 yuan, 10,000 yuan, 20,000 yuan, 50,000 yuan, after the tax reform should be 90 yuan, 290 yuan, 1590 yuan, 9090 yuan, compared with the monthly levy of 3500 yuan, the corresponding tax reduction ratio is 73.9%, 61%, 490%, 18.8%.
It is worth noting that due to holidays, the wages that should be paid in October according to law by various units at the end of September can be applied to the new basic deduction fees and tax rates.
To this end, the withholding client software used by the tax department has provided the corresponding tax calculation function, but the corresponding tax still needs to be declared and paid during the statutory filing period.
Good two: low tax rate grade distance is obviously large
In addition to raising the starting point, the new tax schedule will be applied from October 1.
The seven tax rates of wages and salary income are the same as before, and there is no change, but the tax rate level has changed significantly, and the three-grade low tax rate of 3%, 10%, and 20% has been significantly expanded, and the tax rate margin of 25% has been reduced, while the three higher tax rates of 30%, 35% and 45% remain unchanged.
It is worth noting that the tax law has also adjusted the tax rates of production and operation income, of which the lower limit of the highest 35% tax rate has been increased from 100,000 yuan to 500,000 yuan.
This means that individual businesses and sole proprietorships will benefit from tax reform.
"From the early assessment of individual tax cuts for Shanghai taxpayers, the majority of taxpayers will fully feel the dividends of individual tax reform, especially for low- and middle-income people.
Lan Min, head of the personal income tax department of the Shanghai Municipal Taxation Bureau of the State Administration of Taxation, said.
Benefit 3: Tax service is more convenient and optimized
Since the promulgation of the new personal income tax law, the Shanghai Municipal Tax Department has carried out a series of comprehensive and extensive tax publicity actions.
On the one hand, we will carry out "one-to-one, point-to-point" policy guidance for key tax sources and key enterprises.
Pudong New Area Tax Bureau has visited Apple Trade (Shanghai) Co., Ltd., Alipay (China) Network Technology Co., Ltd., Red Star Meikailong Home Group Co., Ltd. and other large enterprises, these enterprises have a large number of employees, withholding and payment workload, large tax amount, tax departments take the initiative to guide, answer questions; Xuhui District Tax Bureau visited the region's large labor enterprises Zhongzhi Financial Consulting Co., Ltd., Zhongzhi Shanghai Economic and Technical Cooperation Company, etc.
On the other hand, for the general public taxpayers, carry out "all-round, multi-dimensional, three-dimensional" tax policy push.
Use Shanghai tax official website, WeChat public account, Weibo and other channels to push policy hotspots in a timely manner to ensure that policy publicity is in place.
At the same time, since September 28th, Shanghai Tax WeChat public number on-line 12366 intelligent consulting platform, through the "artificial + intelligent" tax service consulting, to carry out "targeted" intelligent integrated tax reform publicity services.
