As a defender of the international order and a practitioner of multilateralism, China's actions are becoming more and more powerful in the multilateral arena of the United Nations.
We will mediate international hotspots, address climate change, participate in peacekeeping operations, vigorously reduce poverty and alleviate poverty, and help other countries implement the 2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development.
